title: Wrath of Umbar: Gondorian Naval Ship Under Attack - Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
The pirates of Umbar are known for their great raids against Gondor.  But instead of raiding their lands, they now get read to capture and board a Gondorian Ship.  Gondor is heavily out numbered, and must use strategic defenses to win this navel battle.  Enjoy the Battle :D

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
